 speak: "ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ, 1234567890", peak.ttf, ruleset: "WeLoveMilo"

now, piglin piglin piglin piglin piglin piglin piglin piglin piglin, set piglins - milo "YES"

